                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-433" type="surname" value="M'PHERSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-433" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN M'PHERSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Thomas Read, linen-draper, of the Commercial-road. On the 1st of May I was standing outside the shop door, minding the things—the prisoners and another young woman came to the shop, looked about the things, then walked to Mr. Stephen son's—I saw Hedger go to the farther end of the shop, and attract the boy's attention while Ryan took a pair of stays, and walked away with them down Exmouth-street—they had been talking together before they went in—I went and told Mr. Stephenson.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430508-name-434" type="witnessName">
