                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-434" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES STEPHENSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a linen-draper. I received information, went down Exmouth-street, and saw Ryan going up Charles-street—she ran two or three yards, took the stays from under her shawl, and threw them into a fore-court—I stopped her, and took them up—they are mine.</p>
